{
  "stem": "7938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we also had some help from the-- from the people who worked in the camp-- in the-- in the-- in the-- whenever a request came in, there was, like, an-- like, an-- you had to be-- somebody had to give you an advice to go there and to allow you to go there.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these people-- what they call [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These people, we knew some people from there, and they helped us, also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So together, as long as somebody wanted us, they put us-- they sent us there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started working in a tool shop on a-- on a one of the [INAUDIBLE] machines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I learned this very quickly in one day, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The good part of it was that we worked only during daytime, because otherwise, there were three shifts-- two shifts, actually.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two shifts, not three.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked always daytime, except at night when you needed-- when some emergency was and some tool broke down.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we had to go there during the night, and to repair it or to start making a new one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife-- my brother-in-law worked also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He worked also in the factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was on the main room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an engineer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was his part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] He was the first helper to the engineer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Schindler worked every day, and he knew everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So far was he willing to help that if he knew that some people are smokers and they didn't have a cigarette, he started a cigarette and he threw it away.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, he couldn't give it to anybody because he was afraid that he will be approached by the Gestapo [INAUDIBLE] for this type of behavior, which once happened to him later.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he was freed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
